settings.favor.tabs: Icon categories that are displyed first on tabs, need to be category such as ant-design or material-symbols, etc.
settings.favor.icons: Icons in my favorites, need to be in the [category]:[name] format.
settings.favor.group: Icon category selected by default on tabs, default is empty. If it's empty, the ALL category will be opened.
settings.code-type: The code type used when copying or inserting icon code.
